{"tid":2431061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【左膠又贏】知名兒童繪畫本作者蘇斯博士作品涉種族歧視 宣布停止出版","createTime":"2021-03-03T11:15:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T11:29:32.000Z","uid":310914,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1ee7b696d910329552f497e5b2e05f779439a30d","tid":2431061,"uid":310914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:15:49.000Z","msg":"【星島綜合報道】知名繪本作家蘇斯博士（Dr. Seuss）所著作6本兒童繪畫書本，因涉及種族歧視而停止出版。<br />\n<br />\n3月2日是全美閱讀日（ National Read Across America Day），也是兒童漫畫家蘇斯博士生日。不過，蘇斯博士的公司「Dr. Seuss Enterprises」週二發佈一則聲明，表示因為涉及種族歧視，蘇斯博士的六本繪本，包含 「McElligot&rsquo;s Pool」 、「On Beyond Zebra!」、「Scrambled Eggs Super!」、「And to Think That I Saw It on Mulberry Street」、「 The Cat&rsquo;s Quizzer」和「If I Ran the Zoo」將停止出版。<br />\n<br />\n聲明中提到，這些書錯誤的描繪方式傷害了人們，他們承諾停止銷售這些書，同時強調蘇斯博士公司支持所有不同社區與家庭。<br />\n<br />\n蘇斯博士是美國著名的作家及漫畫家，代表作有《帽子裡的貓》、《綠火腿加蛋》等，他一生總共出版60幾本作品，更被譯成30種語言，並在1984年獲得普立茲（Pulitzer Prize）特別貢獻獎。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.singtao.ca/4801908/2021-03-02/news-%E3%80%90%E8%A6%96%E9%A0%BB%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E3%80%91%E7%9F%A5%E5%90%8D%E5%85%92%E7%AB%A5%E7%B9%AA%E7%95%AB%E6%9C%AC%E4%BD%9C%E8%80%85%E8%98%87%E6%96%AF%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E4%BD%9C%E5%93%81%E6%B6%89%E7%A8%AE%E6%97%8F%E6%AD%A7%E8%A6%96+%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E5%87%BA%E7%89%88/?variant=zh-hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.singtao.ca%2F4801908%2F2021-03-02%2Fnews-%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%25A6%2596%25E9%25A0%25BB%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%259F%25A5%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2585%2592%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E7%25B9%25AA%25E7%2595%25AB%25E6%259C%25AC%25E4%25BD%259C%25E8%2580%2585%25E8%2598%2587%25E6%2596%25AF%25E5%258D%259A%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E4%25BD%259C%25E5%2593%2581%25E6%25B6%2589%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E6%2597%258F%25E6%25AD%25A7%25E8%25A6%2596%2B%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%25B8%2583%25E5%2581%259C%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%2589%2588%2F%3Fvariant%3Dzh-hk&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiX7P2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=c2399812\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.singtao.ca/4801908/2021-03-02/news-%E3%80%90%E8%A6%96%E9%A0%BB%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E3%80%91%E7%9F%A5%E5%90%8D%E5%85%92%E7%AB%A5%E7%B9%AA%E7%95%AB%E6%9C%AC%E4%BD%9C%E8%80%85%E8%98%87%E6%96%AF%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E4%BD%9C%E5%93%81%E6%B6%89%E7%A8%AE%E6%97%8F%E6%AD%A7%E8%A6%96+%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E5%87%BA%E7%89%88/?variant=zh-hk</a>"},{"pid":"3f666834cb3640b01b56ac2e1f3da5c3a82501c4","tid":2431061,"uid":310914,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:16:15.000Z","msg":"大愛包容，左膠又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2158cb530da4365fba84d45e1ea014e0a680fb9e","tid":2431061,"uid":351978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:17:01.000Z","msg":"種族主義者大權當道，死都拗返生，成日對號入座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲話要同下一代灌輸正確嘅價值觀，真係cls"},{"pid":"9cfbc2f18025641a39c8a23546491ce13c02d0e7","tid":2431061,"uid":351978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2158cb530da4365fba84d45e1ea014e0a680fb9e","tid":2431061,"uid":351978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:17:01.000Z","msg":"種族主義者大權當道，死都拗返生，成日對號入座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲話要同下一代灌輸正確嘅價值觀，真係cls"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:17:40.000Z","msg":"實際上呢班左膠就已經係種族主義者<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09d489a43abbec24cb630dbdfd6780cb89c2c7d3","tid":2431061,"uid":351978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f666834cb3640b01b56ac2e1f3da5c3a82501c4","tid":2431061,"uid":310914,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:16:15.000Z","msg":"大愛包容，左膠又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:19:25.000Z","msg":"歪風不可擋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.